Summary: Spotted while sitting on tailgate in parking lot.
divs: Sighting Details I was sitting on my tailgate in the parking lot last night at 8:20pm. I noticed an object that was not there a few minutes before. At first it looked like a box kite.Then it changed shape & looked like a regular triangle kite. Then it changed shape again .This time it appeared like a metal framed box with a small cylinder type top.By this time I was getting pretty scared. I rubbed my eyes & it was gone that quick& made no sound at all.I had just taking a picture with my cell phone when I noticed it.But it was noticable in photo. Myt first thought was a kid had got a kite caught on a power line. But I soon realized that was not what I was seeing.But by its actions it was not a kite at all. I can't explain it.
